# Global llmquery Function Example

## Basic Usage
{{ llmquery(prompt="What is the capital of France?", model="gpt-4") }}

## Using Variables
{% set question = "What are three interesting facts about " + topic + "?" %}
{{ llmquery(prompt=question, model="gpt-4", temperature=0.8) }}

## Multiline Prompt
{{ llmquery(
    prompt="""Create a short poem about:
    - Season: {{ season }}
    - Theme: {{ theme }}
    - Style: {{ style }}
    """,
    model="gpt-4",
    temperature=0.9,
    max_tokens=200
) }} 